title: The Source Presents Hip Hop Hits Volume 1 [1997] 320kbps
description:
Album Info

In addition to being the nation's number one music magazine and hip-hop's most credible source of information, The Source has made its first contribution to recorded music with THE SOURCE PRESENTS HIP HOP HITS, VOLUME 1, eighteen popular rap songs from 1997 compiled into one package. This compilation represents all facets of the hip-hop genre, and features a diverse line-up of artists from all across the country.
